{"tid":1042341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以色列總檢察長發正式通知 擬控總理內坦亞胡貪污","createTime":"2019-03-01T13:17:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T13:20:57.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a57eeb6c7d45e6228ca291ca198551149087dd","tid":1042341,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T13:17:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190301/large/1551392896_cb60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190301%2Flarge%2F1551392896_cb60.jpg&h=abaa2b7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內坦亞胡指針對他的貪污指控是獵巫行動。(路透社)<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0301 05:58<br />\n<br />\n以色列總理內坦亞胡（Benjamin Netanyahu）面臨貪污起訴。總檢察長曼德爾布利特（Avichai Mandelblit）周四表示，打算起訴內坦亞胡。<br />\n內坦亞胡是首位在任以色列總理收到面臨起訴的正式通知。<br />\n警方一年前宣佈搜集到足夠證據，證明內坦亞胡涉及「貪污、詐騙、背信」等罪名，建議檢察部門起訴他。<br />\n司法部表示，4月9日大選之後，將聆訊是否落案起訴內坦亞胡，屆時他可向德爾布利特提出申辯。聆訊可能歷時數月。<br />\n內坦亞胡尋求連任，但在野黨表明，內坦亞胡一旦被起訴，就算當選也應下台。<br />\n德爾布利特表示，內坦亞胡是否要辭職，由最高法院決定。<br />\n內坦亞胡在黃金時間電視新聞中，語帶憤怒發表聲明，指貪污指控是有人為罷免他而設計出來的政治獵巫行動。<br />\n英國廣播公司／路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190301/59316326\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190301%2F59316326&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=5c933fb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190301%2F59316326&h=effd0fe5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190301/59316326</a>"},{"pid":"1e58073c3f143526aaeab603741de480534dd293","tid":1042341,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T13:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4a51d5bf1020b12bcaa4bc611253207e5faf18","tid":1042341,"uid":162535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T13:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />內坦亞胡以前譯名係咪叫內塔尼亞胡？"},{"pid":"a499fb2429e84c998598e70f30185fe1eb5a24e4","tid":1042341,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T13:20:57.000Z","msg":"咁中国日日點算？<br />\n個個貪到出哂面<br />\n明貪明搶嫁啦"}]}